{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6b9aa9e904","title":"关于电台的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1d7db4636a","index":0,"year":1962,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"6b9aa9e904"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40221b5849","type":"paragraph","text":"民主与集中，集中与分散，分散主义首先是中央（指综合部门）农业机械化要搞个文件，二十五年左右实现机械化，同时实现工业化。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"75c5292faf","type":"paragraph","text":"有的同志在困难面前轴下。是消极好，还是鼓足干劲好？是单干，还是集体好？要提超注意。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"9ddb148cd8","type":"paragraph","text":"对困难发生消极情绪是不是思想问题计委、经委、工交各部要加强支援农业。要抓紧改，这是机会，还来得及。计委搞两个文件：支援农业的报告：三个部分：方向，面向农业，支援农业的方针。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"f1a973c5e4","type":"paragraph","text":"关于电台的指示（国庆节在天安门城楼对周恩来同志的一段讲话）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"b82af4f054","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六二年十月一日）","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"1cd452eab1","type":"paragraph","text":"中近东许多国家发生政变。搞政变的人开始就要夺取电台，向全国和全世界说，原政府的声晋人们就听不到了。我们的电台怎么样？是否掌握在可靠的人手里？要从部队调一个强的干部去。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"ec74900013","type":"paragraph","text":"批新华社","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"0af3397433","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六二年）《内部参考》登那么多包产到户的材料是错识的，今后不要再登。办内部参考要有方向38","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"}],"page":{"id":"34674508ae","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6b9aa9e904","start":51,"end":51}},"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40637f084b","type":"title","text":"关于电台的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"541910637a","type":"paragraph","text":"中近东许多国家发生政变。搞政变的人开始就要夺取电台，向全国和全世界说话，原政府的声音人们就听不到了。我们的电台怎么样？是否掌握在可靠的人手里？要从部队调一个强的干部去。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"5c2eea1d7f","type":"subtitle","text":"（国庆节在天安门城楼对周恩来的一段讲话）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"b724a87944","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"}],"page":{"id":"9663f64612","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6b9aa9e904","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"4972326316","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6b9aa9e904","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在天安门城楼上对周恩来讲话的一部分。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4972326316","type":"paragraph","text":"最近中东许多国家发生政变。搞政变的人开始就要夺取电台，向全国和全世界说话，原政府的声音人们就听不到了。我们的电台怎么样？是否掌握在可靠的人手里？要从部队调一个强的干部去。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"},{"id":"dd4e12aa91","type":"title","text":"关于电台的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"6b9aa9e904"